  <brief_title>Comparison of the Efficacy and Satisfaction of Blood Glucose Management Between Continuous Glucose Monitoring Versus Traditional Self-blood Glucose Measurement in Diabetic Patients After Pancreatectomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of the Efficacy and Satisfaction of Blood Glucose Management Between Continuous Glucose Monitoring Versus Traditional Self-blood Glucose Measurement in Diabetic Patients After Pancreatectomy : A Randomized Controlled Open Labeled Trial</official_title>
